EN: This building is tall and magnificent.

ZH: 那位篮球运动员高大有力。
EN: That basketball player is tall and strong.

ZH: 这座山峰高大险峻。
EN: This mountain peak is tall and steep.

ZH: 她抬起头，望着高大的摩天大楼。
EN: She looked up at the tall skyscraper.

